      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-accepting-acceptted" mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, please do that.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Good job.<BR>Since both the Spirit and Crest have been found, I must now prepare the ritual.</html>]]></talk_question>
